snippet.title: Bilattice: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Bilattice is a massive puzzle game featuring over 300 hand-crafted levels. It is OUT NOW on steam, and is planned to be available iOS and Android as well (coming soon).

Join me on Discord: discord.gg/HWFy9mes4t
Play on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2486430/Bilattice/
